'''合成草酸'''

藉由[[草醯乙酸酶|草醯乙酸酶]][[水解|水解]]草醯乙酸可以獲得[[草酸|草酸]]<ref>Gadd, Geoffrey M. "Fungal production of citric and oxalic acid: importance in metal speciation, physiology and biogeochemical processes" Advances in Microbial Physiology (1999), 41, 47-92.</ref>：
:oxaloacetate + H<sub>2</sub>O <math>\rightleftharpoons</math> oxalate + acetate

